NAME
    Parser::VBA::DocComment - Extract documentation comments from Visual Basic
    for Applications source files

    See "extract".

EXPORT
    Nothing by default; ":all" for everything; otherwise, any of the functions
    listed below.

FUNCTIONS
  extract
    Extract comments.  Usage:

        my $comment_arrayref = Parser::VBA::DocComment::extract($source);

    $source is anything that can be passed to the "io_from_any" function in
    IO::Handle::Util.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests through the web interface at
    <https://github.com/cxw42/Parser-VBA-DocComment/issues>.  I will be
    notified, and then you'll automatically be notified of progress on your
    bug as I make changes.

